and this paranormal stuff.

1895
01:27:15.980 --> 01:27:16.940
and I don't. But...

1896
01:27:19.776 --> 01:27:22.070
No. I don't believe
in that stuff.

1897
01:27:22.153 --> 01:27:24.405
but I still wish we never
went camping that weekend.

1898
01:27:25.990 --> 01:27:27.116
[Kacie] We moved to Portland.

1899
01:27:28.159 --> 01:27:29.786
I know it sounds superstitious.

1900
01:27:29.869 --> 01:27:32.497
but it just seemed like
that whole county was cursed.

1901
01:27:39.128 --> 01:27:41.256
[producer]

1902
01:27:41.339 --> 01:27:43.049
I have no idea.

1903
01:27:43.132 --> 01:27:46.552
[producer]

1904
01:27:46.636 --> 01:27:48.304
What do you want me to say?

1905
01:27:48.388 --> 01:27:50.682
He was part
of some apocalypse cult

1906
01:27:50.765 --> 01:27:54.310
