six-million-year-old leech god?

1907
01:27:54.394 --> 01:27:56.396
Thorn of Time. Kaliban?

1908
01:27:58.439 --> 01:28:01.192
That's not something you put
in a police report. pal.

1909
01:28:01.276 --> 01:28:02.735
That's not going to help
the families

1910
01:28:02.819 --> 01:28:05.321
try and bring closure
and heal from this mess.

1911
01:28:07.991 --> 01:28:10.451
What I can say
for sure is this.

1912
01:28:10.535 --> 01:28:12.287
Leslie Sykes was a monster.

1913
01:28:13.538 --> 01:28:15.540
We caught him
and we killed him.

1914
01:28:17.542 --> 01:28:18.793
[producer]

1915
01:28:21.045 --> 01:28:23.089
As Lexi likes to say.

1916
01:28:23.172 --> 01:28:25.300
same shit. different day.

1917
01:28:27.135 --> 01:28:28.344
Same shit. different day.

1918
01:28:29.804 --> 01:28:31.139
